DataProvider
@Deprecated(since="1.21.4", forRemoval=true) public abstract class BlockStateProvider extends Object implements DataProvider
已过时, 待删除: 此 API 元素将从以后的版本中删除。
Use Vanilla's providers ModelProvider
Data provider for blockstate files. Extends BlockModelProvider so that blockstates and their referenced models can be provided in tandem. In 1.21.4 Mojang exposed their data generators for their models. So it should be feasible to just use theirs. If you find something lacking feel free to open a PR so that we can extend it.
